<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 21:13:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国总理可能在访问巴基斯坦期间为北京资助的机场揭幕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-could-inaugurate-beijing-funded-airport-pakistan-during-visit-2024-10-13/</link><description>信息部长阿陶拉·塔拉尔周日告诉记者，中国总理李强可能会在下周访问巴基斯坦期间为巴基斯坦俾路支省的一个中资机场启用运营。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 11:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-could-inaugurate-beijing-funded-airport-pakistan-during-visit-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>东盟敦促尽早就南海规则达成一致，结束缅甸暴力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-urges-early-accord-south-china-sea-code-end-myanmar-violence-2024-10-13/</link><description>东南亚领导人周日呼吁迅速就基于国际法的南海行为准则达成一致，同时要求缅甸立即停止战斗并进行包容性和平谈判以结束内战。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 07:28:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-urges-early-accord-south-china-sea-code-end-myanmar-violence-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>台湾发现中国航母，中国军事视频称“已做好战斗准备”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-spots-chinese-carrier-china-military-video-says-prepared-battle-2024-10-13/</link><description>中国不排除使用武力将台湾置于其控制之下。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 07:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-spots-chinese-carrier-china-military-video-says-prepared-battle-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>岑浩辉当选澳门候任行政长官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sam-hou-fai-elected-chief-executive-designate-macau-2024-10-13/</link><description>政府周日表示，前法官岑浩辉当选中国澳门候任行政长官，使他成为毗邻香港、以赌场为主的地区的领导人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 05:11:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sam-hou-fai-elected-chief-executive-designate-macau-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>越南与中国领导人会晤签署农产品贸易、支付等10项协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-china-sign-10-documents-during-chinese-premiers-visit-hanoi-2024-10-13/</link><description>在中国总理李强对河内进行为期三天的访问期间，越南和中国周日签署了从农业合作到跨境二维码支付等十项协议，这两个邻国寻求加强关系。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 04:29:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-china-sign-10-documents-during-chinese-premiers-visit-hanoi-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>9月份中国通货紧缩压力加大消费者通胀降温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-consumer-inflation-cools-sept-ppi-deflation-deepens-2024-10-13/</link><description>中国9月份消费者通胀意外放缓，而生产者价格通缩加剧，加大了北京方面迅速推出更多刺激措施以重振疲弱需求和不稳定经济活动的压力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 01:48:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-consumer-inflation-cools-sept-ppi-deflation-deepens-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员指责俄罗斯和中国阻止亚洲领导人发表声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-accuses-russia-china-blocking-asia-leaders-statement-2024-10-12/</link><description>一位美国官员表示，他们的反对主要是针对有争议的南海问题上的措辞。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 22:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-accuses-russia-china-blocking-asia-leaders-statement-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理在河内同意加强与越南的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-hanoi-agrees-boost-ties-with-vietnam-2024-10-12/</link><description>越南政府表示，越南和中国周六同意加强防务和安全合作，尽管两国在南海存在多年的海上争端。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 17:29:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-hanoi-agrees-boost-ties-with-vietnam-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>台湾中华航空公司表示新飞机订单没有政治压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/taiwans-china-airlines-says-no-political-pressure-new-aircraft-order-2024-10-12/</link><description>台湾中华航空公司董事长周六表示，在决定是否购买波音或空客飞机以更新其长途机队方面，该公司并未面临任何政治压力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 11:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/taiwans-china-airlines-says-no-political-pressure-new-aircraft-order-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>尽管局势紧张，台湾人仍涌向中国宗教节日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwanese-flock-china-religious-festival-despite-tensions-2024-10-12/</link><description>本周，一千多名台湾朝圣者涌向中国东南部的福建省参加宗教节日，这是两岸文化交流的罕见实例，但有可能因政治紧张局势而蒙上阴影。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 10:31:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwanese-flock-china-religious-festival-despite-tensions-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告欧盟不要单独进行电动汽车价格谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-not-affect-ev-tariff-talks-with-separate-price-negotiations-2024-10-12/</link><description>中国周六敦促欧盟不要就中国制造的电动汽车在欧盟销售的价格进行单独谈判，警告称这将“动摇双边关税谈判的基础”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 10:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-not-affect-ev-tariff-talks-with-separate-price-negotiations-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责总统讲话后威胁采取更多贸易措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-threatens-taiwan-with-more-trade-measures-after-denouncing-presidents-2024-10-12/</link><description>赖清德表示，中华人民共和国无权代表台湾。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 07:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-threatens-taiwan-with-more-trade-measures-after-denouncing-presidents-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出财政刺激措施以重振增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-fiscal-stimulus-measures-revive-growth-2024-10-12/</link><description>中国财政部周六公布了一项财政刺激计划，旨在重振疲软的经济并实现政府的增长目标，但没有透露新措施的规模。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 06:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-fiscal-stimulus-measures-revive-growth-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国的刺激信息让投资者望而却步</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stimulus-message-leaves-investors-wanting-though-hanging-onto-hope-2024-10-12/</link><description>投资者有充分的理由对北京将花费多少保持谨慎。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 05:51:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stimulus-message-leaves-investors-wanting-though-hanging-onto-hope-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对中国经济刺激政策的通报反应冷淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-investor-reactions-briefing-chinas-finance-ministry-stimulus-2024-10-12/</link><description>中国周六表示，将“大幅增加”政府债务发行，为低收入人群提供补贴、支持房地产市场并补充国有银行资本，以推动重振疲弱的经济增长。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 03:24:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-investor-reactions-briefing-chinas-finance-ministry-stimulus-2024-10-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>